

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5500

### Find products
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/gpt/match-product
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description":"tubo pvc 40 de 4\" "
}

### Products overview
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/gpt/analysis/products/overview

### Family distribution
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/gpt/analysis/products/family-distribution?top=15

### Prefix patterns
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/gpt/analysis/products/prefix-patterns?top=20

### First word analysis
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/gpt/analysis/products/first-word-analysis?top=200

### First word normalization report
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/gpt/analysis/products/first-word-normalization-report?topReview=50

### Category candidates
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/gpt/analysis/products/category-candidates

### Category conflicts
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/gpt/analysis/products/category-conflicts?limit=100

### Normalization preview
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/gpt/analysis/products/normalization-preview?limit=20&offset=0

### Normalization preview by bucket
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/gpt/analysis/products/normalization-preview?limit=20&offset=0&categoryBucket=TUBO_PLASTICO

### Normalized batch
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/gpt/analysis/products/normalized-batch?limit=20&offset=0

### Normalized batch by bucket
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/gpt/analysis/products/normalized-batch?limit=20&offset=0&categoryBucket=VALVULA

### Missing EAN batch
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/gpt/analysis/products/missing-ean-batch?limit=20&offset=0

### Missing EAN batch by bucket
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/gpt/analysis/products/missing-ean-batch?limit=20&offset=0&categoryBucket=TUBO_ACERO

### Missing EAN stored in Neon
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/gpt/analysis/products/missing-ean-stored?limit=20&offset=0

### Sync normalized batch to Neon
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/gpt/analysis/products/sync-normalized-batch?limit=20&offset=0

### Sync normalized batch to Neon by bucket
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/gpt/analysis/products/sync-normalized-batch?limit=20&offset=0&categoryBucket=CODO

### Sync all normalized products
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/gpt/analysis/products/sync-normalized-all?limit=200&startOffset=0

### Sync all normalized products by bucket
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/gpt/analysis/products/sync-normalized-all?limit=10&startOffset=0&categoryBucket=VALVULA

### Generate AI technical summaries for 10 steel pipe products
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/gpt/analysis/products/generate-technical-summaries?limit=10&offset=0&categoryBucket=TUBO_ACERO&onlyMissing=true

### Generate enriched AI technical summaries for 10 steel pipe products with web search
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/gpt/analysis/products/generate-technical-summaries?limit=10&offset=0&categoryBucket=VALVULA&onlyMissing=false&mode=enriched


### List product images
GET http://localhost:5500/api/gpt/analysis/products/e467e5a3-927e-4790-9072-7551db3fcc89/images

### Replace product images
POST http://localhost:5500/api/gpt/analysis/products/e467e5a3-927e-4790-9072-7551db3fcc89/images
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "images": [
    {
      "storage_url": "https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcQ9ZSnse6q1Qdywi4uGnfF-MJrf6SInTaqngaWD35dN8Q&s=10",
      "file_name": "1.jpg",
      "mime_type": "image/jpeg",
      "alt_text": "Vista principal del producto",
      "sort_order": 1,
      "is_primary": true,
      "image_type": "GALLERY",
      "storage_provider": "INTERNAL"
    },
    {
      "storage_url": "https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcT8hIQyIbA6VMR8IY2sSsPSPr28y3Ck65HeHCLuaVNX4w&s=10",
      "file_name": "2.jpg",
      "mime_type": "image/jpeg",
      "alt_text": "Vista lateral del producto",
      "sort_order": 2,
      "is_primary": false,
      "image_type": "GALLERY",
      "storage_provider": "INTERNAL"
    }
  ]
}


### Product detail
GET http://localhost:5500/api/gpt/analysis/products/a52fd184-5e87-4465-b9e4-b8d3e2b02377/detail


### Technical summary status
GET http://localhost:5500/api/gpt/analysis/products/technical-summary-status

### Technical summary status by bucket
GET http://localhost:5500/api/gpt/analysis/products/technical-summary-status?categoryBucket=TUBO_ACERO&limit=20&offset=0

### Vector catalog v2 preview (read-only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/vector-catalog/preview?limit=10

### Vector catalog v2 preview - tuberia only (read-only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/vector-catalog/preview?scope=TUBERIA&limit=10

### Vector catalog v2 preview - steel pipes only (read-only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/vector-catalog/preview?scope=TUBO_ACERO&limit=10

### Vector catalog v2 index one steel pipe (writes only to proscai-catalog-v2)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/vector-catalog/index-test
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ean": "TCC1/240"
}

### Index all eligible steel pipes in the v2 catalog index
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/vector-catalog/index
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "scope": "TUBO_ACERO"
}

### Check the background index job
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/vector-catalog/index/status
